{
  "texts": [
    "[185] that enables road users to send and receive feedback on their driving behaviors through V2V communication.",
    "On the one hand, a driver can express his appreciation and disapproval towards nearby drivers about their polite and impolite driving behavior by gestures.",
    "On the other hand, he can receive others' evaluations through audio and visual feedback.",
    "With the help of a driving simulator, the system is demonstrated to exert a positive influence on driving behaviors.",
    "Regulation ScenariosExperimental scenarios are particularly important for design, verification, and validation efforts."
  ]
}